  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Falling Down XR</strong> — a collection of atmospheric VR arenas with no long introductions or story.</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >5 VR ACTION ARENAS:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• Wild West – revolver gunfight</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• Zombie Subway – survive the infected train</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• Tower of Fear – cult escape</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• Cubic City – VR platforming</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• Ciphergram – cryptography puzzle</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2590670/extras/2ea678eb090d6a41faf96b05d03b924b.avif?t=1772908572\" width=1170 height=250 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Wild West — One Against the City</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You are pinned down in the center of the city. Thirty armed bandits occupy rooftops and streets. You have only a revolver and seconds to return fire. Use cover, shoot ahead of the enemy, and clear the city. You stand at the epicenter of lawlessness. There is no way back.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2590670/extras/b2246c89b452f20bd41b414566eef2d4.poster.avif?t=1772908572\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2590670/extras/b2246c89b452f20bd41b414566eef2d4.webm?t=1772908572\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2590670/extras/b2246c89b452f20bd41b414566eef2d4.mp4?t=1772908572\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Bullet Subway — Stop It or Die</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You are trapped inside a speeding subway train turned into a deadly trap. <br>Your only chance to survive is to break through to the driver’s cabin and stop the train before it derails.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The cars are swarming with zombies. Time is against you. <br>Tight spaces leave no room to maneuver. There is no way back.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2590670/extras/b2a0907cb8594663650b49437e7d20ea.poster.avif?t=1772908572\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2590670/extras/b2a0907cb8594663650b49437e7d20ea.webm?t=1772908572\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2590670/extras/b2a0907cb8594663650b49437e7d20ea.mp4?t=1772908572\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Tower of Fear — A Path to Freedom Through Fear</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Waking up in chains is only the beginning. <br>Somewhere deep inside the temple, a sacrifice is being prepared.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Break free and make your way through the corridors of an ancient labyrinth. <br>One wrong move — and the darkness will claim you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Silence presses in, height steals your balance. <br>Control your fear — it is the only path to freedom.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2590670/extras/139fe7285562336cfc0fd6cf611358b8.poster.avif?t=1772908572\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2590670/extras/139fe7285562336cfc0fd6cf611358b8.webm?t=1772908572\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2590670/extras/139fe7285562336cfc0fd6cf611358b8.mp4?t=1772908572\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>CubicCity — Reality Broken Into Blocks</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In a single moment, a familiar мегacity turns into an endless cubist dream. <br>There is no ground beneath your feet — only fragments of geometry floating in the void.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This VR platformer challenges your vestibular system, <br>forcing you to overcome vertigo and distorted space.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Reach the center of the anomaly and restore order. <br>This is not just a game — it is a walk through the strangest dream of your life.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2590670/extras/71fe2a0fc77baef14c20f0859af490ee.poster.avif?t=1772908572\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2590670/extras/71fe2a0fc77baef14c20f0859af490ee.webm?t=1772908572\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2590670/extras/71fe2a0fc77baef14c20f0859af490ee.mp4?t=1772908572\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Ciphergram — Cipher Warfare</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Become a cryptographer and change the course of the war in Europe.<br>You operate a cipher machine in an underground bunker.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every keystroke decides fates. Precision and speed are mandatory.<br>One mistake — and an officer removes you from duty.<br><br>The cipher machine, encrypted messages, and historical communication flow are fully localized across 9 languages — each with its own alphabet and typing layout.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2590670/extras/52b9168182549bde8614a5e5303f041a.poster.avif?t=1772908572\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2590670/extras/52b9168182549bde8614a5e5303f041a.webm?t=1772908572\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2590670/extras/52b9168182549bde8614a5e5303f041a.mp4?t=1772908572\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >More arenas are already in development, including:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• Special Forces Training</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• Flight of the Phoenix</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• Magic Battle in a Haunted Graveyard</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• Prison Escape</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Falling Down XR</strong> — a collection of atmospheric VR arenas with no long introductions or story.</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >5 VR ACTION ARENAS:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• Wild West – revolver gunfight</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• Zombie Subway – survive the infected train</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• Tower of Fear – cult escape</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• Cubic City – VR platforming</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• Ciphergram – cryptography puzzle</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2590670/extras/2ea678eb090d6a41faf96b05d03b924b.avif?t=1772908572\" width=1170 height=250 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Wild West — One Against the City</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You are pinned down in the center of the city. Thirty armed bandits occupy rooftops and streets. You have only a revolver and seconds to return fire. Use cover, shoot ahead of the enemy, and clear the city. You stand at the epicenter of lawlessness. There is no way back.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2590670/extras/b2246c89b452f20bd41b414566eef2d4.poster.avif?t=1772908572\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2590670/extras/b2246c89b452f20bd41b414566eef2d4.webm?t=1772908572\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2590670/extras/b2246c89b452f20bd41b414566eef2d4.mp4?t=1772908572\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Bullet Subway — Stop It or Die</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You are trapped inside a speeding subway train turned into a deadly trap. <br>Your only chance to survive is to break through to the driver’s cabin and stop the train before it derails.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The cars are swarming with zombies. Time is against you. <br>Tight spaces leave no room to maneuver. There is no way back.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2590670/extras/b2a0907cb8594663650b49437e7d20ea.poster.avif?t=1772908572\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2590670/extras/b2a0907cb8594663650b49437e7d20ea.webm?t=1772908572\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2590670/extras/b2a0907cb8594663650b49437e7d20ea.mp4?t=1772908572\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Tower of Fear — A Path to Freedom Through Fear</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Waking up in chains is only the beginning. <br>Somewhere deep inside the temple, a sacrifice is being prepared.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Break free and make your way through the corridors of an ancient labyrinth. <br>One wrong move — and the darkness will claim you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Silence presses in, height steals your balance. <br>Control your fear — it is the only path to freedom.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2590670/extras/139fe7285562336cfc0fd6cf611358b8.poster.avif?t=1772908572\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2590670/extras/139fe7285562336cfc0fd6cf611358b8.webm?t=1772908572\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2590670/extras/139fe7285562336cfc0fd6cf611358b8.mp4?t=1772908572\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>CubicCity — Reality Broken Into Blocks</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In a single moment, a familiar мегacity turns into an endless cubist dream. <br>There is no ground beneath your feet — only fragments of geometry floating in the void.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This VR platformer challenges your vestibular system, <br>forcing you to overcome vertigo and distorted space.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Reach the center of the anomaly and restore order. <br>This is not just a game — it is a walk through the strangest dream of your life.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2590670/extras/71fe2a0fc77baef14c20f0859af490ee.poster.avif?t=1772908572\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2590670/extras/71fe2a0fc77baef14c20f0859af490ee.webm?t=1772908572\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2590670/extras/71fe2a0fc77baef14c20f0859af490ee.mp4?t=1772908572\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Ciphergram — Cipher Warfare</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Become a cryptographer and change the course of the war in Europe.<br>You operate a cipher machine in an underground bunker.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every keystroke decides fates. Precision and speed are mandatory.<br>One mistake — and an officer removes you from duty.<br><br>The cipher machine, encrypted messages, and historical communication flow are fully localized across 9 languages — each with its own alphabet and typing layout.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.ak